Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:39.89,ED中文,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}被我将光芒紧握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:43.18,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（中山动物园）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便当顺带的小菜要什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢煎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢腊肠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  螃蟹和章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,节日里就是要吃寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三角的三角的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时是圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,里面也是圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  饭团吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记东西或是迟到可是不行的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「4月28日  圆圆的卷心菜」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在山吹高中等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来看哦
